name: Siemens Journey into the industrial metaverse

metadata.name: #0001 Journey into the industrial metaverse
metadata.description:
Join us as we embark on our journey into the industrial metaverse and become the owner of a unique piece of Siemens. Together, we’re reliving some of the most iconic innovations from Siemens’ 175-year history. Each NFT has been inspired by creative stories from the past and provides an outlook into the future generated with an AI and original historical data from Siemens.

Terms and conditions: https://siemens.com/175years-NFT-terms-and-conditions
